awards.description:
Poetry: 
* Troya, Papyrus & Utopia Poetry Awards categorized in Dutch Literary Awards

Emancipation, Empowerment & Gender Equality: 
* Women INC. CORDAID Best Emancipation Initiative Award (Black Tulip); 
* Zami (2007) & Triomf Award (2008) (third price; LF Foundation)

Youth Leadership & Diversity: 
* Selected as one of the top 10 ‘Green Gamechangers’ in the Colourful Top 100 list 2017 (De Kleurrijke Top 100)
* DJ100 2016, selected as one of the 100 forerunners and most sustainable youth leaders in The Netherlands;
* Public Award Contest Inspiration for Integration, De Baak Leadership & Management Centre VNO/NCW; 
* Cosmogirl Born to Lead Awards, Inspirator; 
* &-Campaign Award, 'Best Initiative for Leadership in Youth Empowerment'​, Dutch Ministry of Housing, Communities & Integration;
* 'Libelle Star Nomination'​ for resilient women serving society behind the scenes;

Academic Excellence & Civic Engagement: 
* Emerald & HETL Outstanding Doctoral Research Awards 2020 in Leadership & Organization Development; 
* Member Green Brain Network with 121 sustainability scientists;
* ECHO Award 'University Student of the Year 2007' (Scholarship UCLA) 
* Utrecht University Student of the Year Award for Extraordinary Achievements in Academic Excellence, Leadership & Civic Engagement 2009; 
* HSPHuygensScholarship for Academic Excellence awarded by the Dutch Minister of Education, Culture & Science; 
* 1st international recipient of the Commonwealth Scholarship for doctoral studies at the University of Notre Dame Australia: International Postgraduate Research Scholarship & Australian Postgraduate Award (APA/UPA) & IFFRS Scholarship;

Leadership Development: 
* Leadership & Complexity; Leading in An Age of Uncertainty Course Bursary, Schumacher College;
* Notre Dame Leadership Program (UNDA, co-designer program, speaker & coach); 
* Gross National Happiness & the Inner Dimensions of Social Transformation Leadership Program Bursary, GNH Centre, Bhutan;
